{"id":236024,"date":"2024-02-01T11:29:04","date_gmt":"2024-02-01T05:59:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/?p=236024"},"modified":"2024-02-02T18:00:40","modified_gmt":"2024-02-02T12:30:40","slug":"sita-soren","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/","title":{"rendered":"Sita Soren Wiki, Age, Husband, Children, Family, Biography &amp; More"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\" wp-image-236025 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren.jpg\" alt=\"Sita Soren\" width=\"474\" height=\"416\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren.jpg 683w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren-300x264.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 474px) 100vw, 474px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>Sita Soren is an Indian politician. She is a member of the Jharkhand Mukti Morcha. In 2019, she became a 3-time member of the Jharkhand Legislative Assembly. She is the daughter-in-law of Jharkhand Mukti Morcha chief <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/shibu-soren\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Shibu Soren<\/a> and the wife of Durga Soren. She is also the National general secretary of Jharkhand Mukti Morcha.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_62 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Contents<\/p>\n<label for=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce143d2337\" class=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-label\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/label><input type=\"checkbox\"  id=\"ez-toc-cssicon-toggle-item-65bce143d2337\"  aria-label=\"Toggle\" \/><nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#WikiBiography\" title=\"Wiki\/Biography\">Wiki\/Biography<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Physical_Appearance\" title=\"Physical Appearance\">Physical Appearance<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Family\" title=\"Family\">Family<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Parents_Siblings\" title=\"Parents &amp; Siblings\">Parents &amp; Siblings<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Husband_Children\" title=\"Husband &amp; Children\">Husband &amp; Children<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Other_relatives\" title=\"Other relatives\">Other relatives<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Hemant_Soren\" title=\"Hemant Soren\u00a0\">Hemant Soren\u00a0<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Shibu_Soren\" title=\"Shibu Soren\u00a0\">Shibu Soren\u00a0<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Religion\" title=\"Religion\">Religion<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-10\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Address\" title=\"Address\">Address<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-11\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#SignatureAutograph\" title=\"Signature\/Autograph\">Signature\/Autograph<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-12\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Career\" title=\"Career\">Career<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-13\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Controversies\" title=\"Controversies\">Controversies<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-14\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Arrested_in_horse-trading_case\" title=\"Arrested in horse-trading case\">Arrested in horse-trading case<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-15\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Criminal_Cases\" title=\"Criminal Cases\">Criminal Cases<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-16\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Car_Collection\" title=\"Car Collection\">Car Collection<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-17\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Assets_Properties\" title=\"Assets &amp; Properties\">Assets &amp; Properties<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-18\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Movable_Assets\" title=\"Movable Assets\">Movable Assets<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-19\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Immovable_Assets\" title=\"Immovable Assets\">Immovable Assets<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-20\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Salary\" title=\"Salary\">Salary<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-21\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#Net_Worth\" title=\"Net Worth\">Net Worth<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-22\" href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/sita-soren\/#FactsTrivia\" title=\"Facts\/Trivia\">Facts\/Trivia<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WikiBiography\"><\/span>Wiki\/Biography<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Sita Soren also known as Sita Murmu was born on Saturday 21 February 1976 (<strong>age 48 years; as of 2023<\/strong>). Her zodiac sign is Pisces. She pursued her schooling in a Jharkhand Academic Council School.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Physical_Appearance\"><\/span>Physical Appearance<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Height (approx.):<\/strong> 5&#8242; 7&#8243;<\/p>\n<p><strong>Hair Colour: <\/strong>Black<\/p>\n<p><strong>Eye Colour: <\/strong>Black<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Sita-Soren.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-236386\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Sita-Soren.jpg\" alt=\"Sita Soren\" width=\"295\" height=\"404\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Sita-Soren.jpg 584w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Sita-Soren-219x300.jpg 219w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 295px) 100vw, 295px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Family\"><\/span>Family<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Parents_Siblings\"><\/span><strong>Parents &amp; Siblings<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Sita Soren&#8217;s father, B.N. Majhi, is A retired Indian Oil Corporation Limited official. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236024_1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236024_1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.telegraphindia.com\/jharkhand\/law-catches-up-with-sita-s-father-in-odisha\/cid\/1428830\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Telegraph<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236155\" style=\"width: 420px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren-with-her-father.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236155\" class=\" wp-image-236155\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren-with-her-father.jpg\" alt=\"Sita Soren with her father\" width=\"410\" height=\"272\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren-with-her-father.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren-with-her-father-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren-with-her-father-768x510.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 410px) 100vw, 410px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236155\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sita Soren with her father<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Husband_Children\"><\/span><strong>Husband &amp; Children<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Sita Soren&#8217;s husband, Durga Soren, was a politician. He passed away due to kidney ailments on 21 May 2009. Sita Soren has three daughters, Jayshree Soren, Rajshree Soren, and Vijayshree Soren.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236153\" style=\"width: 370px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-husband-Durga-Soren.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236153\" class=\" wp-image-236153\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-husband-Durga-Soren.jpg\" alt=\"Sita Soren's husband Durga Soren\" width=\"360\" height=\"387\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-husband-Durga-Soren.jpg 600w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-husband-Durga-Soren-279x300.jpg 279w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 360px) 100vw, 360px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236153\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sita Soren&#8217;s husband Durga Soren<\/p><\/div>\n<div id=\"attachment_236152\" style=\"width: 366px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-daughters.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236152\" class=\" wp-image-236152\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-daughters.jpg\" alt=\"Sita Soren's daughters\" width=\"356\" height=\"274\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-daughters.jpg 780w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-daughters-300x231.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-daughters-768x591.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 356px) 100vw, 356px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236152\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sita Soren&#8217;s daughters<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Other_relatives\"><\/span>Other relatives<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Hemant_Soren\"><\/span><strong>Hemant Soren\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Sita Soren&#8217;s brother-in-law, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/hemant-soren\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hemant Soren<\/a>, is the former chief minister of Jharkhand.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236383\" style=\"width: 378px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Hemant-Soren.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236383\" class=\" wp-image-236383\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Hemant-Soren.jpg\" alt=\"Hemant Soren\" width=\"368\" height=\"245\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Hemant-Soren.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Hemant-Soren-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Hemant-Soren-768x512.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 368px) 100vw, 368px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236383\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hemant Soren<\/p><\/div>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Shibu_Soren\"><\/span><strong>Shibu Soren\u00a0<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>Sita Soren&#8217;s father-in-law, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/shibu-soren\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Shibu Soren<\/a>, is the former chief minister of Jharkhand and member of Rajya Sabha representing Jharkhand and the leader of Jharkhand Mukti Morcha.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236384\" style=\"width: 346px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Shibu-Soren.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236384\" class=\" wp-image-236384\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Shibu-Soren.jpg\" alt=\"Shibu Soren\" width=\"336\" height=\"449\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Shibu-Soren.jpg 598w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Shibu-Soren-224x300.jpg 224w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 336px) 100vw, 336px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236384\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Shibu Soren<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Religion\"><\/span>Religion<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Sita Soren follows Hinduism.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Address\"><\/span>Address<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Dhurwa, Sector 3, House No F34, Ranchi, India<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"SignatureAutograph\"><\/span>Signature\/Autograph<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<div id=\"attachment_236075\" style=\"width: 303px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-signature.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236075\" class=\" wp-image-236075\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-signature.jpg\" alt=\"Sita Soren's signature\" width=\"293\" height=\"135\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-signature.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-signature-300x138.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Sorens-signature-768x353.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 293px) 100vw, 293px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236075\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sita Soren&#8217;s signature<\/p><\/div>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Career\"><\/span>Career<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>In 2009, after the demise of her husband, Durga Soren, Sita contested in the 2009 Jharkhand Legislative Assembly Elections from the Jama constituency. She won the elections with a margin of 12706 votes. The same year, she was also appointed as the National general secretary of Jharkhand Mukti Morcha.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236182\" style=\"width: 455px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren-during-an-election-rallly.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236182\" class=\" wp-image-236182\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren-during-an-election-rallly.jpg\" alt=\"Sita Soren during an election rally\" width=\"445\" height=\"251\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren-during-an-election-rallly.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren-during-an-election-rallly-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/Sita-Soren-during-an-election-rallly-768x433.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 445px) 100vw, 445px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236182\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sita Soren during an election rally<\/p><\/div>\n<p>In 2014, she again contested for the same seat and won the elections with a margin of 2306 votes. In 209, she contested the Jharkhand Legislative Assembly Elections from the Jama constituency for the third time and won the elections against BJP&#8217;s Suresh Murmu with a margin of 2426 votes. In 2021, along with her daughters, Rajshree, and Vijayshree, Sita started an NGO to honour her husband named as Durga Soren Sena.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Controversies\"><\/span>Controversies<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Arrested_in_horse-trading_case\"><\/span><strong>Arrested in horse-trading case<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>In 2012, Sita Soren was accused of accepting a bribe to vote for a particular candidate in the Rajya Sabha Elections of 2012, a case was registered against her for the same in the High Court of Jharkhand. In 2014, Sita Soren filed a plea in the High Court to dismiss the criminal proceedings that had been initiated against her, claiming that she had immunity under Article 194(2) of the Constitution; however, her plea was rejected. In 2014, during the CBI investigation, Sita abducted her assistant as he turned approver and was later recovered from her residence which led to registering an abduction case against her. In February 2014, she was sent to jail.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_236380\" style=\"width: 508px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Sita-Soren-taken-in-police-custody.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-236380\" class=\" wp-image-236380\" src=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Sita-Soren-taken-in-police-custody.jpg\" alt=\"Sita Soren taken in police custody\" width=\"498\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Sita-Soren-taken-in-police-custody.jpg 800w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Sita-Soren-taken-in-police-custody-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/Sita-Soren-taken-in-police-custody-768x514.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 498px) 100vw, 498px\" \/><\/a><p id=\"caption-attachment-236380\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sita Soren was taken into police custody<\/p><\/div>\n<p>She managed to obtain regular bail from the apex court in this case on 28 March 2014. On 11 September 2014, she was released from the jail on bail. Later, the case was appealed to the Supreme Court. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236024_1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236024_1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/timesofindia.indiatimes.com\/india\/sita-soren-to-walk-out-of-jail-after-six-months\/articleshow\/42271213.cms?from=mdr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Times of India<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Criminal_Cases\"><\/span><strong>Criminal Cases<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>2 charges related to bribery (IPC Section-171E)<\/li>\n<li>1 charge related to Punishment of criminal conspiracy (IPC Section-120B)<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Car_Collection\"><\/span>Car Collection<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Sita Soren owns a Mahindra Scorpio Jeep.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Assets_Properties\"><\/span>Assets &amp; Properties<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Movable_Assets\"><\/span><span id=\"Movable_Assets\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>Movable Assets<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Cash: Rs. 10,15,000<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Bank Deposits: Rs. 3,56,909<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Motor Vehicles: Rs. 1,36,27,523<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Jewellery: Rs. 1,45,000<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Bonds, Debentures and Shares in Companies: Rs. 53,81,533<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<ul>\n<li>Other assets, such as values of claims\/interests: Rs. 1,15,858<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Immovable_Assets\"><\/span><span id=\"Immovable_Assets\" class=\"ez-toc-section\"><\/span><strong>Immovable Assets<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Residential Buildings: Rs. 50,00,000<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><strong>Note:<\/strong> The given estimates of movable and immovable assets are according to financial year 2014-2015. It excludes the assets owned by her husband and dependents. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236024_1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236024_1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.myneta.info\/jharkhand2014\/candidate.php?candidate_id=1072\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">My Neta<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Salary\"><\/span>Salary<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Sita Soren earns Rs. 2.88 Lakhs as a Member of the Jharkhand Legislative Assembly. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236024_1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[4]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236024_1_4\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/zeenews.india.com\/india\/mla-salary-in-jharkhand-legislators-strike-gold-with-monthly-income-of-2-88-lakhs-and-lavish-perks-2644837.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Zee News<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Net_Worth\"><\/span>Net Worth<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Sita Soren&#8217;s net worth for 2014-2015 was estimated to be Rs. 15,496,765. <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236024_1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[5]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236024_1_5\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/myneta.info\/jharkhand2014\/candidate.php?candidate_id=1072\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">My Neta<\/a><\/span><\/span> It excludes the net worth of her husband and dependents (minors).<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"FactsTrivia\"><\/span>Facts\/Trivia<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Sita Soren is always in the headlines for her derogatory comments and accusations against her family members including <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/hemant-soren\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hemant Soren<\/a>. In January 2024, Sita Soren led a rift among the MLAs of the ruling coalition party after Hemant Soren was arrested by ED, reportedly the senior MLAs held a meeting in Raanchi, where they wanted to make Hemant Soren&#8217;s wife, <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/kalpana-soren\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Kalpana Soren<\/a>, the next chief minister of Jharkhand; however, despite being an MLA from the party Sita along with a few other MLAs protested by not attending the meeting. In an interview, she talked about the incident and claimed that she was more deserving than Kalpana for the role of chief minister. She said,<br \/>\n<blockquote><p>I would like to ask why only Kalpana Soren, who is not even an MLA and has no political experience, under what circumstances her (Kalpana&#8217;s) is being touted as the next chief minister when there are so many senior leaders in the party. I will strongly protest any move to make her CM. There are several senior leaders in the party, who could be given the rein. If they wanted to elect from a family, I am the senior-most in the house and have been an MLA for around 14 years.&#8221; <span class=\"footnote_referrer relative\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"  on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false),footnotes_container_button_plus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=true),footnotes_container_button_minus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed, force=false)\"><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_236024_1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[6]<\/sup><\/a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text_236024_1_6\" class=\"footnote_tooltip position\" ><a href=\"https:\/\/www.deccanherald.com\/india\/jharkhand\/infighting-in-jharkhands-ruling-family-sita-soren-opposes-any-move-to-make-hemants-wife-kalpana-cm-2873018\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Deccan Herald<\/a><\/span><\/span><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><iframe title=\"Hemant Soren \u0915\u0940 \u092d\u093e\u092d\u0940 Sita Soren \u0939\u0941\u0908\u0902 \u092c\u093e\u0917\u0940, Kalpana Soren \u0915\u094b CM \u092c\u0928\u093e\u0928\u0947 \u0915\u093e \u0915\u093f\u092f\u093e \u0935\u093f\u0930\u094b\u0927 | Jharkhand\" width=\"1060\" height=\"596\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/wYLiWbPAKWk?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>In January 2024, after her protests against her own family and party, Sita Soren was named the <a href=\"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/aparna-yadav\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Aparna Yadav<\/a> of Jharkhand.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div class=\"489bcfb86580b123547338c91db0eff2\" data-index=\"3\" style=\"float: none; margin:3px 0 3px 0; text-align:center;\">\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\"\r\n     style=\"display:block\"\r\n     data-ad-format=\"autorelaxed\"\r\n     data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-6769524711517462\"\r\n     data-ad-slot=\"2473600074\"><\/ins>\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"font-size: 0px; height: 0px; line-height: 0px; margin: 0; padding: 0; clear: both;\"><\/div><div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_label_expand_236024_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">References<\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_plus_236024_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[+]<\/span><span><\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" id=\"footnotes_container_button_minus_236024_1\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button collapsed\" on=\"tap:footnote_references_container_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_plus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed),footnotes_container_button_minus_236024_1.toggleClass(class=collapsed)\">[\u2212]<\/span><\/p><\/div> <div id=\"footnote_references_container_236024_1\" class=\"collapsed\"><table class=\"footnotes_table footnote-reference-container\"><caption class=\"accessibility\">References<\/caption> <tbody> \r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_236024_1_1\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>1<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.telegraphindia.com\/jharkhand\/law-catches-up-with-sita-s-father-in-odisha\/cid\/1428830\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Telegraph<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_236024_1_2\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>2<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/timesofindia.indiatimes.com\/india\/sita-soren-to-walk-out-of-jail-after-six-months\/articleshow\/42271213.cms?from=mdr\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">The Times of India<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_236024_1_3\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>3<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.myneta.info\/jharkhand2014\/candidate.php?candidate_id=1072\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">My Neta<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_236024_1_4\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>4<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/zeenews.india.com\/india\/mla-salary-in-jharkhand-legislators-strike-gold-with-monthly-income-of-2-88-lakhs-and-lavish-perks-2644837.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Zee News<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_236024_1_5\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>5<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/myneta.info\/jharkhand2014\/candidate.php?candidate_id=1072\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">My Neta<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index_combi pointer\"><a id=\"footnote_plugin_reference_236024_1_6\" class=\"footnote_backlink\"><span class=\"footnote_index_arrow\">&#8593;<\/span>6<\/a><\/th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.deccanherald.com\/india\/jharkhand\/infighting-in-jharkhands-ruling-family-sita-soren-opposes-any-move-to-make-hemants-wife-kalpana-cm-2873018\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\">Deccan Herald<\/a><\/td><\/tr>\r\n\r\n <\/tbody> <\/table> <\/div><\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Sita Soren is an Indian politician. She is a member of the Jharkhand Mukti Morcha. In 2019, she became a 3-time member of the Jharkhand Legislative Assembly. She is the daughter-in-law of Jharkhand Mukti Morcha chief Shibu Soren and the wife of Durga Soren. She is also the National general secretary of Jharkhand Mukti Morcha. Wiki\/Biography Sita Soren also known as Sita Murmu was born on Saturday 21 February 1976 (age 48 years; as of 2023). Her zodiac sign is Pisces. She pursued her schooling in a Jharkhand Academic Council School. Physical Appearance Height (approx.): 5&#8242; 7&#8243; Hair Colour: Black <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":73,"featured_media":236025,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[4],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/236024"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/73"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=236024"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/236024\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":236975,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/236024\/revisions\/236975"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/236025"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=236024"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=236024"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/wikibio.in\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=236024"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}